   Andie wore a high-necked black lace top with a small black crop-top underneath, leaving some of her toned torso exposed. She paired the frilled garment with stylish wide-legged black trousers. The actress accessorised with a glitzy handbag and wore black sandals for a summery look. She wore her long grey hair down in natural waves and opted for a smokey makeup look, with some bold liner to bring out her brown eyes.  